{"TopicId":168159,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Nodes of maneuvers cant appears","CreatedByName":"Swap","CreatedById":183266,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-03T13:57:15Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Swap","CreatedById":183266,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-03T13:57:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#212121;font-size:16px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003EI just bought KSP yesterday, and I can not create nodes of maneuvers, my apoapsis points should be blue except that they are gray, so I can not create a node by clicking.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#212121;font-size:16px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003ECan someone help me?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-03T19:30:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/183266-swap/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022183266\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/183266-swap/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Swap\u003C/a\u003E, and welcome aboard!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m gonna guess you\u0027re playing on Career mode. You\u0027ll need to upgrade the Tracking Station before you can make maneuver nodes. Hope this helps!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spricigo","CreatedById":166502,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-04T01:26:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso need to upgrade Mission control.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-04T16:36:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust to build on the answers provided by \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/123837-dman979/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022123837\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/123837-dman979/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Dman979\u003C/a\u003E and \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/166502-spricigo/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022166502\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/166502-spricigo/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Spricigo\u003C/a\u003E above:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nWhen you upgrade the Tracking Station, then the trajectories will be shown in blue instead of gray, and you\u0027ll have more information about them in map view.\u00A0 But you won\u0027t be able to create maneuver nodes yet.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nWhen you \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Ealso\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E upgrade Mission Control, then you\u0027ll have maneuver nodes.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you try a sandbox game (as opposed to career), everything\u0027s all fully-upgraded for you when the game starts, so in sandbox you have maneuver nodes available from the very start.\u00A0 But in a career game, you need to upgrade the buildings.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}